{"tid":1730806,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【今晚死守｜理大決戰】獨家！理大勇武會議錄音曝光：不能撤退，我咪死喺度囉！","createTime":"2019-11-17T14:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T15:27:20.000Z","uid":22609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9691a18551b604f03decc7459197d654b2f9a46f","tid":1730806,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"【今晚死守｜理大決戰】獨家！理大勇武會議錄音曝光：不能撤退，我咪死喺度囉！<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_708307_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_708307_0&d=sw6tlk2lcpT%2BYldK84vytFyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=d5ae30b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_708307_0&h=dd0b3d0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_708307_0</a><br />\n<br />\n警方今日晚上已將理大重重包圍，封鎖所有出入口，部分理大示威者於開會期間，表示也許無法守住理大，想強攻或撤退卻被重重包圍，只餘下死守一途。「各區都有狗，唯有死路一條 ，咁我咪死喺度囉！」<br />\n<br />\n從今晨約十時開始，警察以水炮車、銳武裝甲車以音波炮攻擊、連環催淚彈等圍攻理大，直至現時，攻勢仍未停止。<br />\n<br />\n有示威者表示，由於理大有四個入口，又沒有增援，人手嚴重不足，已有心理準備會被捕。<br />\n<br />\n然而，前線士氣依然高漲，更有前線示威者於通往紅磡站的天橋向銳武裝甲車投擲汽油彈，令車身著火。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：梁越<br />\n<br />\n攝影：王晴<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_708307_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_708307_0&d=sw6tlk2lcpT%2BYldK84vytFyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=d5ae30b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_708307_0&h=dd0b3d0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_708307_0</a>"},{"pid":"a6822384c4d02be8304851fd9e603a8a5566dae1","tid":1730806,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883dabe73f9d5b265664f5314ce320b0e3f674f2","tid":1730806,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201